quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"Ntamahoro arimwo muri vyinshi bumvikanyeko mu mabanga yabo atari bamwe bategeka abandi gutanga imperezwa canke kugira ineza canke guhuza hagati y’abantu, rero uwuzogira gutyo arondera impuhwe z’Imana uyo muntu tuzomuha impembo niniya cane"
  4,115,"Uwuzohakana intumwa y’Imana munyuma yaho yamaze kumu bonekera n’uburongozi hanyuma agakurikira inzira itari iyaba Isilamu, twebwe tuzomuhindura iyo azoba yahindukiriye kubwiwe, hanyuma duce tumwinjiza mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu naho n’ahantu habi cane haho umuntu atosubizwa mwo"
  4,116,"Mu vy’ukuri Imana ntigirira ikigongwe c’ukugereranywa n’ikintu kanaka, mugabo niyo igirira ikigongwe kubitari ivyo kuwo yishakiye, rero uwugereranya Imana n’ibindi bintu, ntankeka uyo muntu azoba yarazimiye mukuzimira kuri kure y’ukuri kwama"
  4,117,"Ntibasenga\tmugihe\tbamaze\tguta\tkure\tImana\tatari\tizindi\tMana z’abagore, kandi ntawundi basenga atari Shetani yataye umurongo w’ukuri"
  4,118,"Uwo Imana yavumye nayo ikaba ariyo Shetani yavuze iti:- mu vy’ukuri jewe nzofata bamwe mubantu bazwi mubantu bawe"
  4,119,"Kandi nzobazimiza kandi nzobaha icizere kandi nzobategeka hanyuma bazoca amatwi y’ibikoko vyabo, kandi nzobategeka bahindure ibiremwa vy’Imana, n’uwuzogira Shetani kuba ariyo imu kingira aho gukingirwa n’Imana, azoba yahomvye uruhombo ruri k’umugaragaro"
  4,120,Shetani Ibemerera n’ukwizera kuko Shetani ntibemerera atari ububeshi gusa
  4,121,"Abo nibo ivyicaro vyabo arivyo mu muriro udahera, kandi ntibazoronka ubuhungiro bwo kuva muri uwo muriro udahera"